1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,160
Listen carefully: not everything is solved with sight.

2
00:00:04,160 --> 00:00:08,560
Your goal will be to correctly rebuild a musical sequence.

3
00:00:08,560 --> 00:00:13,240
To do that, you will use the tokens and the terminal buttons.

4
00:00:13,240 --> 00:00:17,240
At the start of each phase, you will hear a song fragment.

5
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:20,800
Then you must reproduce that same fragment,

6
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:23,240
by passing tokens through the terminals.

7
00:00:23,240 --> 00:00:26,960
You may listen to it again as many times as you need.

8
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:29,840
When you think you have found the correct sequence,

9
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:31,440
you will have to register it.

10
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:34,560
With the buttons you can listen, register,

11
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:36,160
or delete a sequence.

12
00:00:36,160 --> 00:00:38,160
This test has two phases.

13
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:39,520
Tune your ear.

14
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:41,360
The music starts now.
